description:
Depth 10-26-2021 by Romero - An exploration into depth of field with sculpture like tubular shapes. The primary layer of beige, aqua, blue & vanilla is set in 3D while the secondary floating layer above of purple, lime green & pink is not. While creating this work I noticed the effect of this is to keep the eye and the brain in contemplation constantly moving between the two layers of the work.

4096X2304 px 6000 DPI
